This solution is build under Visual Studio 2017, .Net Framework Version 4.6.1 and in C# language.

PreConditions

1. Enter Full Name (only First Name is not allowed)
2. Enter Currency in decimals only

Input/Output
The web page form is posted throgh Ajax and the output of the conversion is in the Json string format.

Expected Output
1. If after decimal, it has more than two points, output will be in ones otherwise it will be in tens.
Example
0 - ZERO DOLLAR
1- ONE DOLLARS 
12.123- TWELVE DOLLARS AND ONE TWO THREE CENTS
12.12 - TWELVE DOLLARS AND TWELVE CENTS


Test Cases
The solution has covered 30 test cases.
